caption: A great place to visit with your loved one. 'I love you' is written in loads of languages and it is fun finding yours. When found you have to take a photo and say 'I love you' in your language to your loved one. A truly special occasion in a special and unique place.
This park hosts a wall of love. Love is written every language around the world. Purpose your loved one, kiss each other or hug your loved one, and click some pics

Paris is known as the city of fashion and France is called fashion capital of the world. French designers have long created the most renowned and coveted fashion brands in the world. French clothing industry can be traced as far back as the 17th century. Since then French designers have been dominating the fashion world. The industry's graph was declined during 2nd World War and the USA took the advantage of the opportunity. Hence there was an increasingly significant level of competition arising from both the USA and Italy. But France designer's stylistically innovative and technically exceptional designs have been defeating all its competitors and continued to strengthen the modern fashion world with new concepts and ideas.
